subject: Tennis
lead_paragraph: CoCo Vandeweghe of the United States beat China’s Zheng Jie, 6-2, 6-4, in the final of the Topshelf Open, a grass-court tournament in ’s-Hertogenbosch, the Netherlands, to claim her first WTA title.
